这个看起来可以合起来，另外也不需要 `includes` 了，两个变量 includes 反而会让体积变大：

```tsx
const validOrientation = orientation ===  'horizontal' || orientation ===  'vertical';
const mergedOrientation = validOrientation ? orientation : (defaultVertical ? 'vertical' : 'horizontal');
return [mergedOrientation, mergedOrientation === 'vertical'];
```
